# Sverklo Demo — health audit + badge
Output demo.gif
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 800
Set Height 450
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set Shell "zsh"

Hide
Type "cd ~/projects/research/product/sverklo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "# Run a health audit on any codebase"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "sverklo audit"
Enter
Sleep 12s

Type "# Get a dynamic badge for your README"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Type "sverklo audit --publish"
Enter
Sleep 12s

Sleep 2s
